Ah, that's better.  You're no longer so overloaded.	啊，好多了。你不再負重過度了。
That really hurt.  But it only really hurt for a few moments.  The pain is quite gone now.  So is every other sensation.  Taking quick stock of your condition, you find the reason -- you're dead.  Better run away next time.	那真的很痛。但痛楚只持續了幾秒鐘。現在疼痛已經完全消失，其他知覺也一樣。你快速盤點自己的狀況，找到了原因——你死了。下次最好還是快逃吧。
It is %s.	這是%s。
You can't open %s.	你無法打開%s。
You can't close %s.	你無法關上%s。
The smell is exactly as you would expect.	這氣味正如你所預期的一樣。
You can't move %s.	你無法移動%s。
You wouldn't want to eat %s.	你不會想吃%s的。
You can't get %s.	你無法取得%s。
You can't climb %s.	你無法攀爬%s。
Don't bother trying to talk to %s.	別費心跟%s說話了。
  Quest for Glory II:  Trial By Fire  [%d of %d]	  英雄傳奇 II：烈火試煉  [%d之%d]
You collapse in the hot desert air and never awaken.  Truly it is said that "Water is life itself in a desert land."	你在灼熱的沙漠空氣中倒下，再也沒有醒來。正如人們所說：「在沙漠之地，水就是生命本身。」
You must get water soon, or you will surely die of thirst.	你必須盡快取得水，否則必將渴死。
The dry desert air seems to suck the moisture right out of your body.	乾燥的沙漠空氣似乎正把你體內的水分一點一滴抽走。
Your Reversal spell is wearing thin.	你的反轉法術效力正逐漸減弱。
You thought for a moment that you saw a deadly Fragmentation Bug, but then realize that it is actually the harmless Southern variety.  You squash it under your boot, and it vanishes.	你一度以為看到了致命的「分裂蟲」，但隨即發現那其實是無害的南方變種。你一腳將牠踩扁，牠便消失無蹤。
Great idea.  If you could, you would.	好主意。如果辦得到，你早就做了。
The lamp seems to enjoy that (but it's just your imagination).	那盞燈似乎很享受（不過那只是你的想像）。
You faintly hear "To the left... up... ahh, right there!"  The lamp glows faintly with pleasure, then decides it isn't dark enough to really put on a show, and goes out again.	你隱約聽到「往左…再上面一點…啊，就是那裡！」燈微微發出愉悅的光芒，接著覺得天色還不夠暗、不值得真正表演一番，於是又熄滅了。
It's not as effective as Raseirian Express.	效果不如「拉希爾特快」。
You put on the Ali Fakir Genuine X-Ray Glasses.  Suddenly, everything appears as though you were looking through a veil.	你戴上了阿里·法基爾正宗透視眼鏡。突然間，一切看起來就像隔著一層薄紗。
Ok, you get the empty pot.	好，你拿到了空罐子。
Ok, you get the pot of dirt.	好，你拿到了裝土的罐子。
You have it already.	你已經有這個了。
Ok, you pick up the bag.	好，你撿起了袋子。
There isn't a shield here.	這裡沒有盾牌。
You will have to finish off your opponent first.	你得先解決掉對手才行。
You retrieve your knives and carefully wipe them clean for reuse.	你收回了飛刀，仔細擦拭乾淨以便重複使用。
Ok, you pick %s up.	好，你撿起了%s。
Which one?	哪一個？
You drop your shield.	你放下了盾牌。
O.k.  Your Saurus is now standing on the ground.	好，你的索魯斯現在站在地面上了。
You drop the %s.	你放下了%s。
The silver dagger isn't balanced properly for throwing.	這把銀匕首的重心不適合用來投擲。
You don't have one to throw.	你沒有可以投擲的東西。
That isn't useful here.	這在這裡沒有用。
To do that, you must cast the Levitate spell.	要這麼做，你必須施展「飄浮術」。
You don't need to retreat if you're not in combat.	你不在戰鬥中，不需要撤退。
You're already sneaking.	你已經在潛行了。
Pardon, Effendi.  I don't know how you would use that here.	抱歉，閣下。我不知道那東西在這裡該怎麼用。
You don't need to climb it.	你不需要攀爬它。
You certainly do!	你當然需要！
There is no one here who would appreciate them.	這裡沒有人會欣賞這些。
This is a serious game, %s.	這是場嚴肅的遊戲，%s。
You see no silly clowns here, at least not now.	你在這裡沒看到任何滑稽的小丑，至少現在沒有。
Don't worry about it.  It's all being taken care of.	別擔心，一切都已經處理好了。
Sorry, but there is nothing I can tell you about that.	抱歉，關於那件事我無可奉告。
You really can't rest here.	你真的不能在這裡休息。
This isn't a safe place to sleep.	這裡不是安全的睡覺地方。
Wait a minute!  You can't do that here!!!	等一下！你不能在這裡這麼做！！！
Please, Effendi.  A thousand pardons, but I do not understand	拜託，閣下。萬分抱歉，但我不明白
RM%03d: %s: "%s" 	RM%03d：%s：「%s」 
do you mind if I join you?	你介意我加入你嗎？
 Could you run that by me once more, please? 	 能否請你再說一次？ 
