Development System by: JEFF STEPHENSON ROBERT E. HEITMAN PABLO GHENIS DAN FOY LARRY SCOTT ERIC HART COREY COLE and MARK WILDEN  Special thanks to our long-suffering Beta testers: Neil, Janet, Linda, Gano, Todd, Dan, Paul, Tod, and Lance	開發系統：JEFF STEPHENSON、ROBERT E. HEITMAN、PABLO GHENIS、DAN FOY、LARRY SCOTT、ERIC HART、COREY COLE 與 MARK WILDEN　特別感謝辛苦的 Beta 測試員：Neil、Janet、Linda、Gano、Todd、Dan、Paul、Tod 與 Lance
      DURING THE GAME: Click at the top of the screen or press ESC to use the menus. Additional shortcuts are shown there. Click Right or Shift-Click Left Mouse Button on an object to look at it.       IN TYPING WINDOWS: Arrows, Home and End move the cursor, or click anywhere with the mouse. Ctrl-C clears the line.       IN DIALOG WINDOWS: Select the outlined item with <Enter> and use Tab and Shift-Tab to move between  choices.  Or click with the mouse to select an item.  ESC always cancels. 	      遊戲進行中：點擊螢幕上方或按 ESC 開啟選單，選單上會列出更多快速鍵。點擊滑鼠右鍵，或按住 Shift 點擊滑鼠左鍵可查看物件。       輸入視窗中：方向鍵、Home 與 End 可移動游標，也可用滑鼠點擊任意位置。Ctrl-C 可清除整行。       對話視窗中：按 <Enter> 選取外框標示的項目，用 Tab 與 Shift-Tab 在選項間  切換。  或用滑鼠點擊選取項目。  ESC 一律可取消。 
Placing the index finger of each hand in opposing corners of your mouth, you simultaneously pull your fingers outward, extending and wiggling your tongue vertically.	你把雙手食指分別放在嘴角兩側，同時向外拉扯，並上下擺動伸出的舌頭。
CAUTION:  Do not try this at home!	注意：請勿在家嘗試！
Using both hands, you touch your left knee, your right instep, both temples, and that small spot in between your shoulder blades that always itches.	你用雙手依序碰觸左膝、右腳背、兩側太陽穴，以及肩胛骨之間那個總是發癢的小地方。
You eat some of the magical fruit.  It tastes strange.	你吃了一些魔法水果。味道很奇怪。
Ugh.  You don't want to eat THAT!	噁。你才不會想吃那個！
You'd better not.	你最好別這麼做。
You can't drink that.	你不能喝那個。
I don't know what kind of pill that is.  Remember, just say no to unknown pills.  Your local apothecary can give you advice on safe and sane pill use.	我不知道那是什麼藥丸。記住，來路不明的藥丸一律拒絕。當地的藥師可以給你安全用藥的建議。
You don't have any of those pills.	你沒有那種藥丸。
The only effect is a tingling sensation.  But, if the apothecary is to be trusted, you should be safe from the effects of poison for a while.	唯一的效果是一陣刺痛感。不過，如果藥師的話可信，你應該能暫時免受毒素影響。
The pill makes you thirsty, so you pull out your waterskin.	這藥丸讓你感到口渴，於是你拿出了水袋。
You drink the last drops from your waterskin.  You might want to start looking around for a place where you can refill it.	你喝下了水袋裡最後幾滴水。你該開始找個地方把它裝滿了。
Your water skin is getting much easier to carry.  Unfortunately, that probably means you don't have much water left.	你的水袋變得輕巧許多，好拿多了。可惜這大概表示你剩下的水已經不多了。
After an hour's rest, you feel refreshed.	休息了一小時後，你感到神清氣爽。
You will have to practice some more to improve your lockpicking skill.	你得多加練習，才能提升開鎖技巧。
While it's true that some foods may be bad for your health, *no* food is even worse.  You have, quite literally, starved to death.	雖然有些食物確實對健康不好，但完全*不吃*東西更糟。你就這樣，貨真價實地餓死了。
You don't have any flowers.	你沒有任何花。
You already have the %s.	你已經有%s了。
How many %s do you want?	你想要幾個%s？
You put the %s away.	你把%s收起來了。
You pay for the %s and put %s away.	你付了%s的錢，並把%s收起來了。
You see nothing out of the ordinary.	你沒看到任何異常之處。
What you see doesn't hold your interest.	你看到的東西引不起你的興趣。
You look around and things look normal.	你環顧四周，一切看起來很正常。
It doesn't seem important right now.	現在看起來不太重要。
blah	廢話
Brass Centime%s	銅仙%s
One hundred tiny brass centimes are worth a single Golden Dinar.	一百枚細小的銅仙相當於一枚金第納爾。
Golden Dinar%s	金第納爾%s
The heavy golden Dinar is the coin preferred by nobility.  The front bears the image of Suleiman ben Daoud, Master of the Djinn.	沉甸甸的金第納爾是貴族偏愛的錢幣。正面刻著精靈之主蘇萊曼·本·達伍德的肖像。
Food Ration%s	口糧%s
Broadsword%s	闊劍%s
Dagger%s	匕首%s
Small and sleek local daggers are most useful for throwing or for close fighting.	這種小巧俐落的當地匕首，最適合用於投擲或近身格鬥。
Leather Armor%s	皮甲%s
Shield%s	盾牌%s
Piece%s of Paper	紙張%s
Small Rock%s	小石頭%s
Small rocks, suitable for throwing.  Generously available in rocky, desert areas.	適合投擲的小石頭，在多岩的沙漠地帶隨處可見。
Lock Pick%s	開鎖器%s
Thief's Tool Kit%s	盜賊工具組%s
Your Thief's Tool Kit contains a variety of slim, sharp instruments.  In the right hands, these implements will open any locked (but unbarred) door.	你的盜賊工具組裡有各式細薄鋒利的工具。在行家手中，這些工具能打開任何上鎖（但未加閂）的門。
Thieves' Guild License%s	盜賊公會執照%s
Your Thieves' Guild License authorizes you to do business with Thieves without getting killed by them.	你的盜賊公會執照讓你能與盜賊做生意，而不會被他們殺掉。
Pouch%s of Incense	香料袋%s
Whirl%s of Beard	鬍鬚捲%s
In your pack is a whirl of the Desert Dervish's beard.	你的背包裡裝著一捲沙漠苦行僧的鬍鬚。
Chainmail Armor%s	鎖子甲%s
Magic Rope%s	魔法繩索%s
The Magic Rope you purchased from the Magic Shop looks like an ordinary rope, although it coils tighter and weighs less.	你從魔法商店買來的魔法繩索，外觀就像一條普通繩子，只是盤起來更緊、也更輕。
Gold Coin%s	金幣%s
You still retain golden coins from the land of Spielburg.	你身上還留著來自史畢柏格之地的金幣。
Healing Pill%s	治療藥丸%s
You have healing pills to magically restore your health.	你有可以用魔法恢復生命值的治療藥丸。
Mana Pill%s	法力藥丸%s
You have mana pills to magically restore your magical ability.	你有可以用魔法恢復法力值的法力藥丸。
Vigor Pill%s	體力藥丸%s
You have vigor pills to magically restore your stamina.	你有可以用魔法恢復體力值的體力藥丸。
Dispel Potion%s	解除藥水%s
Map%s	地圖%s
Compass%s	羅盤%s
Fine Sword%s	精良長劍%s
You are carrying a fine sword from the weapon shop of Issur.	你帶著一把來自伊蘇爾武器店的精良長劍。
Bellows	風箱
Flower Bouquet%s	花束%s
Sapphire Pin%s	藍寶石胸針%s
The Kattas gave you this sapphire pin in thanks for your service to their kind.	卡塔族送給你這枚藍寶石胸針，感謝你為他們族群所做的貢獻。
Griffin Feather%s	獅鷲羽毛%s
Scorpion Tail%s	蠍尾%s
The scorpion's tail looks as venomous as it is.	這條蠍尾看起來和實際一樣毒。
